Alastair Mackenzie is a Scottish actor . He was born in 1970 in Trinafour , near Perth . Mackenzie left home at the age of 18 and moved to London . Though best known as a television and film actor , he also has some theatre credits to his name . He lives with his wife , Scottish actress Susan Vidler , with whom he has one daughter , Martha , born in February 2000 . His brother is director David Mackenzie . 